steps.name: Given  verify that user is on para bank customer login page
When  user click on register link
Then  user can see the signup register form
When  user enter a valid firstname as "baby"
When  user enter a valid lastname as "girls"
When  user enter a valid address as "chennai"
When  user enter a valid city as "chennai"
When  user enter a valid state as "tamilnadu"
When  user enter a valid pincode as "600000"
When  user enter a valid phoneno as "1234567890"
When  user enter a valid ssnno as "12345"
Then  user enter a valid username as "babygirls"
Then  user enter a valid password as "12345"
Then  user enter a valid confirmpass as "12345"
And  user finally click on register button
And  user see the successfully registered message
